'''非洲巨鼠屬'''（学名：'''''{{lang|la|Cricetomys}}'''''），亦作'''巨頰囊鼠屬'''<ref name=ichacha>{{cite web |url=http://tw.ichacha.net/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%B0%E5%9B%8A%E9%BC%A0.html |title=非洲巨頰囊鼠英文 - 英語翻譯 |work=ichacha.net 查查綫上詞典 |language=zh |accessdate=2015-06-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304082325/http://tw.ichacha.net/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%B0%E5%9B%8A%E9%BC%A0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是[[哺乳綱|哺乳綱]][[囓齒目|囓齒目]][[馬島鼠科|馬島鼠科]]的一屬，而與非洲巨鼠屬（非洲巨鼠）同科的動物尚有[[南非囊鼠屬|南非囊鼠屬]]（南非囊鼠）、[[長尾巨鼠屬|長尾巨鼠屬]]（長尾巨鼠）等之數種[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]。

==物種==
*''[[Cricetomys_ansorgei|Cricetomys ansorgei]]''
* [[非洲巨頰囊鼠|非洲巨頰囊鼠]] ''Cricetomys gambianus''<ref name=ichacha />：亦作[[非洲巨鼠|非洲巨鼠]]
*''[[Cricetomys_emini|Cricetomys emini]]''
*''[[Cricetomys_kivuensis|Cricetomys kivuensis]]''

==與人類關係==
[[File:HeroRAT_finds_mine.jpg|thumb]][[莫罗戈罗|莫罗戈罗]]接受尋找地雷訓練的「英雄鼠」。]]

非洲巨鼠是一種雜食性動物，體型巨大如貓。過往曾大多起非洲巨鼠襲擊人類嬰孩致死的新聞<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.jgospel.net/news/tech/%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E5%A6%82%E8%B2%93%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%B7%A8%E9%BC%A0%E5%92%AC%E6%AD%BB%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5._gc33674.aspx |title=南非如貓大的非洲巨鼠咬死兩名女童 |date=2011-06-08 |accessdate=2015-06-03 |language=zh-hant |publisher=JGospel |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304094404/http://www.jgospel.net/news/tech/%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E5%A6%82%E8%B2%93%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%B7%A8%E9%BC%A0%E5%92%AC%E6%AD%BB%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5._gc33674.aspx |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/news/3617002/KING-RAT-Shock-photo-of-giant-rodent-blamed-for-child-attacks.html |title=KING RAT: Shock photo of giant rodent blamed for child attacks |trans_title=鼠王：令人震驚的巨鼠被指襲擊兒童 |publisher=[[太陽報_(英國)|太陽報 (英國)]] |year=2011 |accessdate=2015-06-03 |archive-date=2016-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427130704/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/news/3617002/KING-RAT-Shock-photo-of-giant-rodent-blamed-for-child-attacks.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

然而，牠們亦非完全一無是處：牠們雖然體型巨大，但體重輕盈，不足1.5公斤，加上其靈敏的嗅感，所以[[比利時|比利時]]一個以[[坦桑尼亞|坦桑尼亞]]為基地的[[非謀利組織|非謀利]][[非政府組織|非政府組織]][[APOPO|APOPO]]選擇了這種在當地為患的巨鼠訓練來探測[[地雷|地雷]]<ref name="BBC 英伦网 2016">{{cite web | title=非洲巨鼠：受訓成為「掃雷特工隊」 | website=BBC 英伦网 | date=2016-01-05 | url=https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert_fut/2016/01/160105_vert_fut_scratch-and-sniff-mine-detectors | language=zh | access-date=2021-02-07 | archive-date=2020-10-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006214730/https://www.bbc.com/ukchina/trad/vert_fut/2016/01/160105_vert_fut_scratch-and-sniff-mine-detectors | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Wood>{{cite web | last = Wood | first = Ian | title = Rats being used to sniff out land mines | publisher = Telegraph.co.uk | date = 18 December 2007 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/earth/earthnews/3319113/Rats-being-used-to-sniff-out-land-mines.html | accessdate = 2008-11-23 | archive-date = 2009-02-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090226083713/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/earth/earthnews/3319113/Rats-being-used-to-sniff-out-land-mines.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.iol.co.za/index.php?art_id=nw20090129075359379C745562 |title=Giant rats sniff out Mozambique's mines |publisher=''IOL'' |date=2009-01-29 |language=en }}</ref>。然後當巨鼠嗅出地雷所在，就會輕輕扒開所在位置的泥土，而訓練員會給巨鼠一條蕉作獎勵<ref name="apple">{{cite news |url=https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181208/642133 |title=【《大帥哥》老鼠踩爆地雷情節有誤】體重輕難引爆 受訓後能助掃雷 |newspaper=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報 (香港)]] |date=2018-12-08 |access-date=2018-12-09 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2018-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209212542/https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181208/642133 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

這些非洲巨鼠的訓練程序由比利時的Bart Weetjens開發出來，從巨鼠出生後四星期開始。

除了偵測地雷，APOPO亦嘗試利用這些「英雄鼠」的敏銳嗅覺來學習尋找[[肺結痎|肺結痎]]病人：相比於傳統方式每日只可以檢測30到40個樣本，每隻非洲巨鼠每天能夠處理數以百計的樣本<ref name=hero>{{cite web | title = Fighting Tuberculosis | trans_title = 打擊肺結痎 | publisher = herorat.org | url = http://www.herorat.org/en/fightingtuberculosis | accessdate = 2008-11-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080804041055/http://www.herorat.org/en/fightingtuberculosis | archivedate = 2008-08-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

